playtesterp
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
playtesterp

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
playtesterp -  This method returns whether or not the given player is a playtester.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
varargs int playtesterp(mixed person,
int nocre)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^person%^RESET%^ - the player to test
%^BOLD%^optional%^RESET%^ - flag to make it return 0 for creators
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
whether or not the player is a playtester
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/secure/simul_efun.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns whether or not the given player is a playtester.
This will return 1 for creators as well, unless the optional nocre
flag is set.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
adminp, lordp, seniorp, creatorp, liaisonp

.EP

